Class AbstractParamInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.coercer.AbstractParamInfo

    ReflectionParamInfo, SkylarkParamInfo

    public abstract class AbstractParamInfo
extends Object
implements ParamInfo
    Represents a single field that can be represented in buck build files. This base class implements some common logic that is used by both all subclasses

      • traverse

        public void traverse(CellPathResolver cellPathResolver,
                     ParamInfo.Traversal traversal,
                     Object dto)
        Description copied from interface: ParamInfo
        Traverse the value of the field on dto that is represented by this instance.

        If this field has a top level Optional type, traversal begins at the Optional value, or not at all if the field is empty.

        Specified by:
        traverse in interface ParamInfo
        traversal - traversal to apply on the values.
        dto - the object whose field will be traversed.
